{"tid":470772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國製造商：不會向不民主國家出售衝鋒槍","createTime":"2017-11-16T15:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T01:32:40.000Z","uid":5195,"like":304,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"c89bf71c5dacb77fb90d314a60e7625fb5603e8d","tid":470772,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:24:45.000Z","msg":"近日，據俄羅斯軍事等價網報道，德國最大的輕武器製造商HK公司決定不再向北約成員國以外的國家供應其生產的武器裝備，因為向其他國家供應武器很難獲得德國政府的批准。HK公司將向那些民主和無腐敗的國家，同時是北約成員國或夥伴國的國家出售武器，這一立場將會排除該公司與這些國家，如沙特阿拉伯、墨西哥、巴西、印度，甚至是北約成員國但是存在人權問題爭議的土耳其進行武器交易，在被問及對這一立場的態度時，該公司並未作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/military/6k3a5nv.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fmilitary%2F6k3a5nv.html&d=ndziCs%2BJvTtf4JlSxQWcGk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=f4b14566\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/military/6k3a5nv.html</a>"},{"pid":"2e293e82b93f2b20298065d1b065cc64de2cbbfe","tid":470772,"uid":31637,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"好囉, 警犬要用國產走火槍囉"},{"pid":"d324e1b79ed4f542ce69d500046d07713fc63b2a","tid":470772,"uid":10014,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"kknews<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無正source？"},{"pid":"3616d529145a22e0e582a08fd197082fbbe95688","tid":470772,"uid":65530,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7519e1821d22cf1594e39625fb1e36324525ea1a","tid":470772,"uid":144222,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:15:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/heckler-koch-saudi-arabia-german-arms-trade-undemocratic-corrupt-nato-a7444981.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com